{"tid":504871,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"財經法情：輝山乳業擔保人被追2.33億元 (18:44)","createTime":"2017-12-20T13:35:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-21T01:08:58.000Z","uid":17738,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"10fd60f6e85005feca5f5821365683fd18eb13f3","tid":504871,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T13:35:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://m.on.cc/nc/fin/20171220/img/20171220184444fi_p1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.on.cc%2Fnc%2Ffin%2F20171220%2Fimg%2F20171220184444fi_p1.jpg&h=f02a18d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=L%2FuTO2Xyn%2BKc934WAUEEI3Iou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=3d0614ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】為輝山乳業(06863)貸款出任擔保人的4家公司，遭恒生銀行入稟香港高等法院興訟追還約2.33億港元。<br />\n<br />\n4名被告公司是中國輝山乳業控股(香港)、China Huishan Dairy Investments International Ltd.、China Huishan Dairy Holdings International Ltd.，以及Upking Holdings Ltd.。<br />\n<br />\n入稟狀指，欠款源於2015年10月簽立的財務安排協議，當中輝山乳業為借款人，4名被告為擔保人。恒生現追討未還債款約2,966萬美元及利息約24.3萬美元，合共折合約2.33億港元。<br />\n<br />\n傳訊令編號：HCA2924/2017 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.on.cc/nc/fin/20171220/20171220184444fi.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.on.cc%2Fnc%2Ffin%2F20171220%2F20171220184444fi.html&d=L%2FuTO2Xyn%2BKc934WAUEEI3Iou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=23f62f5e\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.on.cc/nc/fin/20171220/20171220184444fi.html</a>"},{"pid":"a7f20b949da40e2244b8795554261c2ee49a67ae","tid":504871,"uid":49588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T01:08:58.000Z","msg":"中國人都唔敢飲中國地獄鬼國出產嘅牛奶產品！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n邊有錢還債！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中國人口裹說著美國人的不是，身體腳編編購買最多美國出產的美鑽臣奶粉！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中國人嘅身體特別誠實！"}]}